                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Saldırı</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">2 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Fiziksel Hasar </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir.</span></p>",
